    <div class="text-hero-wrapper">
      <div class="h1-style">
        <div class="h1-style"><span class="h1-0">Ride Where You Are</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        Traveling on a bike is the greatest way to get around, and Lichen Bike Tours is here to bring people together on
        bicycles and to bring people closer to nature. We love the feeling of waking up in a shelter, dry, in a forest,
        and knowing the entire day will be dedicated to outdoors adventuring. Based in Hudson, NY, we offer guided
        bikepacking trips through the Catskill Mountains that are as short as an overnighter and as long as 5 days.
        Camping not your thing? Expect inn-to-inn trips in 2026, and maybe we saw you on June 28th 2025 at our
        first-ever Beebe & Beyond Gravel Ramble in Hillsdale, NY.
      </div>
    </div>
